content: What are all the medications you are currently taking, including over-the-counter drugs and supplements?
Do you have any known drug allergies?
Have you had any surgeries in the past?
Have you experienced any confusion, drowsiness, or bleeding from your gums or nose recently?
Did you experience any fever, chills, or right upper quadrant pain around the time you started taking the antibiotics or noticed the jaundice?
How severe is the jaw pain now on a scale of 1 to 10, and have you noticed any swelling or redness around the jaw area?
Is the jaw pain still present, or has it completely resolved since you stopped taking the Tylenol?
What is the name of your blood pressure medication, and what dose do you take daily?
